name: Shuper Basket
description:
Shuper is the Mexican word equivalent to hipster. The Shuper Basket is woven from two colors of ribbon, with a bottom stitched over for durability and two straps for runs to the laundromat. Store socks, create a fort for your cat, make a small laundry basket of it, pile in your yarn. 

Measures 13" tall by 11" wide.

name: Super Shuper
description:
If the Shuper Tote is the most popular, this is the secret in house favorite. Wide and long, it's got style and the capacity to haul your groceries home. We're working on a bike-friendly model next, shh. 

New colors coming very soon!

Measures 19x11.5 inches

Shipping included in price.

name: Shuper Tote: Brandy
description:
A favorite, now with long handles! Interwoven ribbons create a super lightweight, bright colored shoulder bag just the right size for a laptop or a good book. Check out the other sizes for shopping bags and larger totes!

Measures 11x11"

Shipping included in price.
